assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Hefei Kewell Power System Co.,Ltd. engages in manufacture and sale of test power supplies and systems in China. It provides DC sources and loads, including programmable series, DC power sources, regenerative DC series, source load power system, high precision EVD series, bidirectional DC power supplies, array simulators, EBD/EBDH series battery packs, charge discharge test power supplies, EVS series battery simulators, KDL series fuel cell specific, and energy recycling DC electronic loads; AC source and loads, which include bidirectional grid simulators, variable frequency series, AC power supplies, and electronic loads; and ATE devices. The company also offers fuel cell test equipment; electric vehicle test, comprising EVS battery simulators, EVD high precision, bidirectional DC power supply, E-motor simulator, source load power system, programmable DC power supplies, powertrain system and e-motor controller test solutions, and DC charging piles. In addition, it provides fuel cell tests, power semiconductor tests, photovoltaic energy storage tests, and power semiconductor and intelligent manufacturing equipment, as well as test systems fuel cell, electrical component test, and general test equipment. Its products are used in industrial fields such as new energy power generation, electric vehicles, fuel cells, and power devices. The company was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Hefei, China.
